---
import { ViewTransitions } from 'astro:transitions';
import Paginated from '../components/Paginated.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="Frequently asked questions about the reasoning toolkit." />
  <title>FAQ â€” reasoningtool</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <ViewTransitions />
</head>
<body>
  <Paginated pageGroup="info" pageIndex={2}>
    <section class="faq">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do I use a skill?</summary>
        <p>Skills can be used with <code>/[skill name]</code>.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Does it load all 367 skills into context at once?</summary>
        <p>No.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is there anything this system <em>shouldn't</em> be used for?</summary>
        <p>Yes.</p>
        <div class="faq-buttons">
          <button class="faq-btn pg-github" data-url="https://github.com/benjam3n/reasoningtool/tree/main/docs/methodology">docs/methodology</button>
          <button class="faq-btn pg-github" data-url="https://github.com/benjam3n/reasoningtool/blob/main/docs/methodology/01_core_principles.md">core principles</button>
          <button class="faq-btn pg-github" data-url="https://github.com/benjam3n/reasoningtool/blob/main/docs/methodology/02_process.md">processes</button>
          <button class="faq-btn pg-github" data-url="https://github.com/benjam3n/reasoningtool/blob/main/docs/methodology/03_capability_guidance.md">capability guidance</button>
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>
  </Paginated>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: var(--sp-2) 0;
  }

  .faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .faq-item summary::before {
    content: '+';
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 1.2em;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform var(--transition);
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::before {
    content: '\2212';
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
    padding-left: calc(1.2em + var(--sp-2));
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .faq-item p a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .faq-item p a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .faq-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4em;
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
    padding-left: calc(1.2em + var(--sp-2));
  }

  .faq-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3em 0.7em;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-accent-subtle);
    transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
  }

  .faq-btn:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .faq-item code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    background: var(--color-code-bg);
    padding: 0.15em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
</style>
